Confident is a very simple dependency analyzer for C/C++ projects.

Build requirements:
	boost-devel >= 1.64.0
	glibc-devel >= 2.26
	libstdc++-devel >= 7.3.1

Build requirements (tools):
	cmake >= 3.14.7
	gcc-c++ >= 7.3.1
	git >= 2.29.2
	graphviz >= 2.40.1
	ninja-build >= 1.10.2
	sed >= 4.2.2

Run-time requirements:
	boost-filesystem >= 1.64.0
	boost-program-options >= 1.64.0
	boost-regex >= 1.64.0
	boost-system >= 1.64.0
	glibc >= 2.26
	libgcc >= 7.3.1
	libstdc++ >= 7.3.1

Run-time requirements (optional):
	cmake >= 3.14.7
	graphviz >= 2.40.1
